{"tid":951814,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會羨慕其他家庭今日做冬","createTime":"2018-12-22T15:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T02:46:30.000Z","uid":25237,"like":120,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ca5f19469053ab5873ed7cac5f8c720e6cb1ca","tid":951814,"uid":25237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"屋企關係差到不得了 個個都貌合神離 莫講話做冬 <br />\n就連普普通通坐低食餐飯都原來係幾年前嘅事<br />\n慢慢開始唔會再記得幾時係冬至<br />\n今日咁啱同事問起幾時做冬先發現原來今日冬至<br />\n次次都唔識點答依啲問題 求其亂答幾句嘢扯開話題<br />\n放工突然想搵個fd食飯 點知個個都要做冬<br />\n最後是但搵間茶記填飽個肚算 <br />\n望住隔離檯一家人齊齊整整 有講有笑 <br />\n就忍唔住流馬尿 擺低錢就跑出去 臨走仲聽到個小朋友問點解個哥哥喊<br />\n<br />\n有時真係好羨慕佢哋"},{"pid":"8e2f501397f60307089bbc8ca6084c891d1a2d11","tid":951814,"uid":25237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d07e4d90e8ebe987fda45cc5c477b6b8c7d21a2","tid":951814,"uid":103168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"加油啊巴打，嘗試吓緩和大家嘅關係？"},{"pid":"972c43a8e245b65a38b3138173b2f0a8400b19ea","tid":951814,"uid":76753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"單親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53abddf9a38aca27b1b2a8a946785e0ddced44dc","tid":951814,"uid":25237,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"5d07e4d90e8ebe987fda45cc5c477b6b8c7d21a2","tid":951814,"uid":103168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"加油啊巴打，嘗試吓緩和大家嘅關係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"好多嘢錯咗就返唔到轉頭 只會越嚟越錯<br />\n家人依種關係 睇落係最親密最重要<br />\n但其實係相反 家人依種關係 更多嘅只係出於習慣"},{"pid":"a2e98f03abdd9bad56331e7a89bd0ffd4cbd7aa1","tid":951814,"uid":25237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"972c43a8e245b65a38b3138173b2f0a8400b19ea","tid":951814,"uid":76753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T16:09:06.00